      • productsSearch

        void productsSearch(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
        This method looks to see what kind of search is needed by the content in the text field. If numbers are detected in the text field then it looks for the part id and returns the Part. If characters are detected then it looks through the names of the products and returns all products equal to the search

        Uses Method:
        • Inventory.lookupProduct(int)
        • Inventory.lookupProduct(String)
        • MainScreenController.capFrstLetOfWords(String)
        Parameters:
        event - mouse click
